{"tid":2394740,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"開餐廳真係唔好搵yahoo宣傳","createTime":"2021-02-04T11:25:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T13:13:03.000Z","uid":109573,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"802370b541b04987323423cea427c585fe2bc9d5","tid":2394740,"uid":109573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:25:23.000Z","msg":"【旺角美食】90後一腳踢開傳統糖水舖 生磨芝麻糊日賣400碗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n年輕人，流行沖咖啡，開caf&eacute;，做甜品，開網店&hellip;..下數一百字，也沒有「傳統中式糖水舖」的份。偏偏在流行文化集中地旺角，開了間光猛簡潔的糖水舖，賣的，也不是cheesecake、梳乎厘班戟、日式刨冰等火紅甜品，而是和打卡絕緣的芝麻糊、合桃露、蕃薯糖水、紅豆沙等。由廚房捧著甜品出來的，又不是叔叔嬸嬸，而是個鍾情美國漫畫的大男孩Jeffrey。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開在後生仔最愛「蒲」的旺角，卻主打傳統中式糖水。<br />\n<br />\n全店僅做14款甜品，<span class=\"red\">重量不重質</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9SXNeUQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9SXNeUQ.jpg&h=ccb072dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇到呢度已經無睇落去：一腳踢開，一腳踢 開，轉做獨立開得唔得？下面又話人重量不重質。<br />\n<br />\n班編輯真係Hea到出汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，定其實得我覺得有問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/amphtml/%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E7%BE%8E%E9%A3%9F-%E4%BB%81%E8%8A%9D%E5%88%9D-%E7%B3%96%E6%B0%B4-%E7%94%9F%E7%A3%A8%E8%8A%9D%E9%BA%BB%E7%B3%8A-223042979.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Famphtml%2F%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E7%25BE%258E%25E9%25A3%259F-%25E4%25BB%2581%25E8%258A%259D%25E5%2588%259D-%25E7%25B3%2596%25E6%25B0%25B4-%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%25A3%25A8%25E8%258A%259D%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E7%25B3%258A-223042979.html&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRAqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=35cf22a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/amphtml/%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E7%BE%8E%E9%A3%9F-%E4%BB%81%E8%8A%9D%E5%88%9D-%E7%B3%96%E6%B0%B4-%E7%94%9F%E7%A3%A8%E8%8A%9D%E9%BA%BB%E7%B3%8A-223042979.html</a>"},{"pid":"b71e05e172aab036ab21d99f082633c591c7426e","tid":2394740,"uid":33359,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:27:30.000Z","